text: Brian Patoir was a cricketer from British Guiana. Brian competed in nine first-class matches for British Guiana. He was born on May 6, 1927 and died on April 12, 1969.Brian Patoir == References == == Other websites == Category:1927 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Guyanese sportspeople Category:Guyanese cricketers
